This is Perl module WWW::HatenaDiary.

INSTALLATION

WWW::HatenaDiary installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell
is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan WWW::HatenaDiary

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

WWW::HatenaDiary documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc WWW::HatenaDiary

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

